# 3-Class Baseline (Structured, Trainable)
# Purpose: Same topology as the crafted 3-class net (includes inhibitory pool),
# with neutral weights that allow training to sculpt robust WTA behavior.

# NEURON <id> <threshold> <leak> <resting>
# CONNECTION <from_id> <to_id> <weight>

# Sensory
NEURON S0 100.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON S1 100.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON S2 100.0 1.0 0.0

# Outputs (include pool N0 for WTA)
NEURON O0 50.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON O1 50.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON O2 50.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON N0 40.0 0.8 0.0  # inhibitory pool (stronger WTA after training)

# Symmetric feedforward: equal drive to all outputs (chance-like start)
CONNECTION S0 O0 35.0
CONNECTION S0 O1 35.0
CONNECTION S0 O2 35.0

CONNECTION S1 O0 35.0
CONNECTION S1 O1 35.0
CONNECTION S1 O2 35.0

CONNECTION S2 O0 35.0
CONNECTION S2 O1 35.0
CONNECTION S2 O2 35.0

# Pool wiring (moderate WTA to enable separation during training)
CONNECTION O0 N0 20.0
CONNECTION O1 N0 20.0
CONNECTION O2 N0 20.0

CONNECTION N0 O0 -25.0
CONNECTION N0 O1 -25.0
CONNECTION N0 O2 -25.0
